snippet.title: Real Pool 3D - iPhone, iPad & Android Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
iOS FREE: https://goo.gl/Nj7UpC
Android FREE: https://goo.gl/PWOYLl

The ultimate fun pool game, challenge your friends to matches or play against the AI players.
The best 3d pool game for iPhone and Android.

Features:
- 8 Ball, 9 Ball and UK 8 Ball.
- Play with the Computer Player.
- Pass & Play with friends.
- 1 or 2 player
- 3 Different Controls.
- Spin / English Control.
- 10 Characters to choose from.
- 3 AI Difficulty Levels.
- 3 Table colors.
- Realistic Physics.
- Stunning 3D graphics.
- GameCenter Support.
- Relaxing Musics.
